---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="和モダン — 地域おこし協力隊DAO">
  <div class="wa">
    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="nav">
      <div class="nav-logo">協力隊DAO</div>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="#about">知る</a>
        <a href="#vision">理念</a>
        <a href="#join">参加する</a>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-vertical">
        <p class="hero-vertical-text">地域と、ともに歩む。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-main">
        <h1>
          <span class="hero-sub">地域おこし協力隊DAO</span>
          つながりが、<br />地域を変える。
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-desc">
          全国の協力隊員がDAOでつながる。<br />
          知恵を共有し、地域の未来を共創する。
        </p>
        <div class="hero-line"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-accent">
        <span class="hero-accent-char">共</span>
        <span class="hero-accent-char">創</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About -->
    <section id="about" class="about">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-label">
          <span class="section-num">01</span>
          <span class="section-title">About</span>
        </div>
        <div class="about-content">
          <h2>地域おこし協力隊DAO<br />とは何か</h2>
          <p>
            地域おこし協力隊の経験者・現役隊員・地域に関わるすべての人をつなぐ、分散型コミュニティです。株式会社あるやうむが運営し、Web3の仕組みを活用しながら、地域課題の解決と新しい価値の創造に取り組んでいます。
          </p>
          <div class="about-stats">
            <div class="stat">
              <span class="stat-num">47</span>
              <span class="stat-label">都道府県</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
              <span class="stat-num">DAO</span>
              <span class="stat-label">自律分散型組織</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
              <span class="stat-num">共創</span>
              <span class="stat-label">隊員 × 地域 × テック</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Vision -->
    <section id="vision" class="vision">
      <div class="vision-bg-text">未来</div>
      <div class="vision-content">
        <span class="section-num">02</span>
        <h2>一人の力は小さくとも、<br />つながれば、地域は動く。</h2>
        <div class="vision-cards">
          <div class="vision-card">
            <div class="vision-card-num">壱</div>
            <h3>知恵の共有</h3>
            <p>各地の協力隊員が持つノウハウ・経験を、コミュニティ全体の資産として蓄積し、次の挑戦者へ受け継ぐ。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="vision-card">
            <div class="vision-card-num">弐</div>
            <h3>越境する協働</h3>
            <p>地域の壁を越えて、共通の課題を持つ隊員同士がプロジェクトを立ち上げ、協働する場を提供。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="vision-card">
            <div class="vision-card-num">参</div>
            <h3>持続する仕組み</h3>
            <p>DAOの仕組みを活用し、特定の誰かに依存しない、持続可能なコミュニティ運営を実現。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section id="join" class="cta">
      <div class="cta-inner">
        <p class="cta-label">Join the DAO</p>
        <h2>あなたの地域の物語を、<br />ここから始めよう。</h2>
        <a href="#" class="cta-button">コミュニティに参加する</a>
        <p class="cta-note">運営: 株式会社あるやうむ</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <a href="/" class="back-link">← デザイン一覧に戻る</a>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .wa {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
    color: #2d2926;
    background: #f7f5f0;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  /* Nav */
  .nav {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 24px 48px;
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(247, 245, 240, 0.9);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .nav-logo {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 32px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
  }

  .nav-links a {
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    transition: opacity 0.3s;
  }

  .nav-links a:hover {
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr 120px;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0 48px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .hero-vertical {
    writing-mode: vertical-rl;
    justify-self: center;
  }

  .hero-vertical-text {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.5em;
    color: #999;
    font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
  }

  .hero-main h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.4em;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: #999;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
  }

  .hero-desc {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 2.2;
    color: #666;
    font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .hero-line {
    width: 60px;
    height: 1px;
    background: #2d2926;
    margin-top: 48px;
  }

  .hero-accent {
    writing-mode: vertical-rl;
    justify-self: center;
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .hero-accent-char {
    font-size: 4rem;
    opacity: 0.04;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* About */
  .about {
    padding: 160px 48px;
    border-top: 1px solid #e0ddd5;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    max-width: 1000px;
  }

  .about-label {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .section-num {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: #bbb;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #999;
  }

  .about-content h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .about-content p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 2.2;
    color: #555;
    font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .about-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 48px;
    margin-top: 48px;
    padding-top: 48px;
    border-top: 1px solid #e0ddd5;
  }

  .stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .stat-num {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #999;
    font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
  }

  /* Vision */
  .vision {
    padding: 160px 48px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #2d2926;
    color: #f7f5f0;
  }

  .vision-bg-text {
    position: absolute;
    right: -20px;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    font-size: 20rem;
    opacity: 0.03;
    font-weight: 700;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .vision-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 1000px;
  }

  .vision-content h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin: 24px 0 64px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .vision-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .vision-card {
    padding: 40px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(247, 245, 240, 0.15);
  }

  .vision-card-num {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0.3;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .vision-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .vision-card p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 2;
    color: rgba(247, 245, 240, 0.6);
    font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .cta {
    padding: 160px 48px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-inner {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cta-label {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #bbb;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .cta h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 18px 48px;
    background: #2d2926;
    color: #f7f5f0;
    font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .cta-note {
    margin-top: 32px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #bbb;
    font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
  }

  .back-link {
    display: block;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 32px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #999;
    border-top: 1px solid #e0ddd5;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    color: #2d2926;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .nav { padding: 16px 24px; }
    .hero {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      padding: 120px 24px 80px;
      min-height: auto;
    }
    .hero-vertical, .hero-accent { display: none; }
    .about { padding: 80px 24px; }
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 32px;
    }
    .about-stats { flex-direction: column; gap: 24px; }
    .vision { padding: 80px 24px; }
    .vision-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .cta { padding: 80px 24px; }
  }
</style>
